 InitCache←{
     ⎕IO←0
     ⍺←10 ⍝ Default depth

     ⍝ Don't reinitialize so that I can compare cold & warm start
     ⍝ performance
     ⍺=≢cache:⍴cache

     ⎕THIS.cache_cols←⊂⍤⍋⍛⌷⍵
     ⍝ ⎕THIS.cache←(≢⍵) ⍺ ⍴ 0
     ⍝ I'm not going to write the code to dynamically add
     ⍝ columns to the cache, so we initialize it to a fixed
     ⍝ number of columns
     ⎕THIS.cache←⍺ 10000⍴0

     ⍴cache
 }
